  Kou3 Gou5 Chiu--si7 Chu5-ai3, si7 cha2-ni5 e5 thoan5-to7 kou3 Chiu Pou7-ha5 Sian-siN e5 cha-bou2-kiaN2. Se3-han3 tit-tioh8 lau7-pe7 eng7 to7-li2 gau5 poe5-iuN2, u7 tit-tioh8 chin ho2 e5 sin3-sim. I e5 hiaN chiu7-si7 Chiu Sek-eng TiuN2-lo2 kap Chiu Hok-choan5 Sian-siN. Ti7 22 hoe3 e5 si5 cho3 kheh, ke3 Gou5 Liong5-bun5 Sian-siN, kap tiong7-hu toa3 12 ni5 ku2; kau3 34 hoe3 e5 si5, put-heng7 tiong7-hu koe3-sin, u7 pang3 3 e5 hau7-seN, chit8 e5 cha-bou2-kiaN2 kau-tai7 i iuN2-chhi7. U7 tu2-tioh8 che7-che7 e5 phaiN2 keng2-gu7, chong2-si7 i oa2-kho3 Siong7-te3 lai5 poe5-iuN2 i sou2 siu7 kau-tai7 e5 chai5-san2. Toa7 hau7-seN Chu2-hui7, hian7-si5 ti7 Tang-kiaN Cho2-tiu7-tian5 Tai7-hak8 cho3 kau3-siu7; te7 2 hau7-seN chiu7-si7 hian7-jim7 Sin-hang7 kau3-hoe7 e5 Thoan5-to7-su Gou5 Gi7-iong2 kun; te7 3 hau7-seN hian7-chai7 Khi2-kho chai7-hak8-tiong, ia7 cha-bou2-kiaN2 si7 ke3 i-seng. E7 kham-tit kong2, Siong7-te3 u7 pang-chan7 i, hou7 i tit-tioh8 seng5-kong. Kou2 lai5 e5 siok8-gu2 kong2, Iong2-ji5 thai7-lo2, hit e5 si5-chun7 i2-keng kau3 lah ! Bo5 phah-sng3 Siong7-te3 m7-chun2 i koh ti7 se3-kan lai5 kan-khou2, khah hoaN-hi2 i tng2-khi3 kap Pe7 saN-kap toa3. Sou2-i2 ti7 4 goeh8 16 jit8, ti7 loan2-jiok8 e5 sin-the2 e5 tiong-kan, Pe7 u7 thau2-pang3 i e5 tioh8-boa5, chhoa7 i tng2-khi3 I tau, hiong2-siu7 57 hoe3. I taN ti7-hia bo5 koh iu-bun7, bo5 koh siong-pi, chhin-chhiuN7 Si--nih sou2 gim5 kong2, 
  Siu7 Chu2 sou2 siok8 cheng3 hiaN-chi2, <BR>  Tiam3 ti7-hia khia7-khi2; <BR>  Si5-si5 o-lo2 goa2 e5 Chu2, <BR>  Siong5 gim5-si (Seng3-si 249 siu2). 
  Chong2-si7 i it-seng u7 3 tiam2 hou7 lan2 tai7-ke thang oh8. 
  1.Gau5 kau3-iok8 chu2-te7. Tui3 tiong7-hu koe3-sin liau2-au7, i e5 taN3 chiu7 kam2-kak chin tang7. U7-si5 hiam2-hiam2 taN bo5 hoat-tit, na7-si7 i u7 oa2-kho3 Siong7-te3, eng7 un-jiu5, khiam-pi kap ki5-to2 ti7 i e5 bo2-seng3-ai3 lai5 kau3-iok8 kiaN2-ji5. U7-si5 chiu7 bian2-le7, u7-si5 chiu7 chek-pi7, u7-si5 chiu7 eng7 bak8-sai2 lai5 kek-le7 kiaN2-ji5. Kau3 kin-na2-jit8 khoaN3-tioh8 in e5 seng5-kong, chiu7 chai lah. 
  2. Gau5 khin5-khiam7. Sui-jian5 m7-si7 chin san3 e5 lang5, chong2-si7 i chin khiam7-iok. Gau5 ke3-ek8 tioh8 chaiN2-iuN7 lai5 eng7 chiN5, chiah e7 thang i5-chhi5 ka-teng5 kap kau3-iok8 chu2-te7. Na7 khoaN3 i e5 khiam7-iok, chin-chiaN3 si7 chit8 e5 ho2 e5 chu2-hu7, gau5 e5 lau7-bo2 lah ! 
  3. Gau5 hok8-sai7 Siong7-te3. Han2-tit khoaN3 i bo5 kau3 pai3-tng5, sui-jian5 u7 sim2-mih8 chou2-tong3, i ia7 si7 poah si5-kan kau-poe5 Siong7-te3. Ui7-tioh8 kiaN2-ji5 e5 seng5-kong, u7 sim2-mih8 oh-tit e5 su7, chiu7 tui3 Siong7-te3 kiu5. Siong5-siong5 ai3 thiam5-cheng7 kau-poe5 Siong7-te3, i liah8 kiN3 Siong7-te3 e5 bin7, cho3 i te7-it ho2 e5 kang. 
  Chong2-si7 taN i tit-tioh8 ho2 e5 siuN2-su3, eng2-oan2 thang khia7-khi2 ti7 Pe7 e5 tau. Goan7 i e5 kiaN2-ji5 oh8 lau7-bo2 e5 ho2 bou5-iuN7, gau5 hok8-sai7 Chu2 bo5 soah. 
  (Tai5-oan5 Kau3-hoe7 Kong-po3 te7 651 ho7, 1939 ni5 6 geh8) 
</CL>
